125
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:43,730
One day,

126
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:46,140
♫Gazes across the expanse of time♫

127
00:07:44,470 --> 00:07:46,230
I'll make him pay blood for blood.

128
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:49,690
♫Love and hate travel through the years♫

129
