What a pity.

142
00:08:46,730 --> 00:08:48,810
These two should've been a perfect match.

143
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:52,160
♫If love has turned into a sharp arrow♫

144
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,040
Why were they unwilling to meet?

145
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:52,430
Such a shame.

146
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:56,660
♫It will pierce the heart's desire♫

147
00:09:02,210 --> 00:09:05,010
How long are you going to keep harassing Conghuan?

148
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:09,100
You don't want your past with Conghuan

149
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,500
